<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Acceso Denegado - Charlotte</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/seguridad/usuarios.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-50">
    <div class="contenedor-dashboard">
      
      <main class="contenido-principal flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-screen w-full">
        
        <div class="text-center max-w-lg p-8 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
            <div class="mb-6">
                <div class="mx-auto w-20 h-20 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center animate-pulse">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-lock text-4xl text-red-500"></i>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                Acceso Restringido
            </h1>
            
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6">
                No tienes los privilegios suficientes para ver esta secci√≥n.
            </p>

            <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-400 p-4 mb-8 text-left rounded-r">
                <div class="flex">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation text-orange-400"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ml-3">
                        <p class="text-sm text-orange-700">
                            Error de permisos (403)
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-sm mt-1 text-orange-800 font-medium">
                            Falta permiso para el recurso: 
                            <span class="font-mono bg-orange-100 px-1 rounded text-orange-900">
                                <%= resource %>
                            </span>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-900 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-gray-500 transition-all duration-200">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left mr-2"></i>
                Regresar
            </a>
        </div>

      </main>
    </div>
   
  </body>
</html>
